01/11/2024,748.505(b)(4) - Individual Standards Evaluated,Individual Standards Evaluated,No,01/18/2024,01/16/2024,Individual Standards Evaluated,Medium,Yes,"During an inspection, 1 of 5 staff files reflected the notarized affidavit was provided and signed but was not completed in the exception area. ","Inspector received email from Administrator with completed notarized affidavit.  Administrator reported in an effort to prevent this from occurring again they have developed a staff file audit, which reflects minimum standards. HR will complete the initial audit on each file. We then have a standing meeting on the first business day of the month where directors will complete a second audit on their employe files, utilizing the minimum standards checklist. The checklist will contain signature lines and dates to indicate who completed the audits and when. This double audit system will reduce the number of oversights and increase accountability significantly. 

"
